# Integer Overflow Detection Patterns

# Basic arithmetic operations without overflow checks
(\w+)\s*\+\s*(\w+)
(\w+)\s*-\s*(\w+)
(\w+)\s*\*\s*(\w+)

# Unsafe math operations
uint\d*\s+\w+\s*\+\s*\w+
uint\d*\s+\w+\s*-\s*\w+
uint\d*\s+\w+\s*\*\s*\w+

# Potential overflow in loops
for\s*\(\s*.*\+\+.*\)
while\s*\(.*\+\+.*\)

# Unsafe external calls that might cause overflow
\.call\{.*value:\s*\w+\}
\.transfer\(\s*\w+\)
\.send\(\s*\w+\) 